OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773821068
OL,3,CShould the UK cancel or delay King's
OL,4,Cstate visit to the White House?
OL,6,FShould King Charles press ahead with
OL,7,Fan official state visit to the USA, at
OL,8,Fa time when President Trump is failing
OL,9,Fto secure any international support
OL,10,Ffor his Iran war and when he
OL,11,Frepeatedly lashes out at the UK and
OL,12,Four European allies?
OL,14,FIt's a problem that someone is soon
OL,15,Fgoing to have to address.
OL,17,FAnd, as much as many think it's the
OL,18,FKing's problem, it's not.
OL,20,FIt's actually an issue for Downing
OL,21,FStreet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
