OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773821068
OL,3,CShould the UK cancel or delay King's
OL,4,Cstate visit to the White House?
OL,6,FThat's because State Visits, both
OL,7,Fincoming ones (think USA, France,
OL,8,FGermany last year) and external ones
OL,9,F(the King most recently visited Italy
OL,10,Fand The Vatican) are decided by the
OL,11,FForeign Office.
OL,13,FTherefore, the Monarch carried them
OL,14,Fout on government advice.
OL,16,FSo, it is wrong to assume that King
OL,17,FCharles and his senior staff at
OL,18,FBuckingham Palace can decide
OL,19,Fthemselves to delay the visit to
OL,20,FWashington DC and New York.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
