CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773821068
OL,3,CShould the UK cancel or delay King's
OL,4,Cstate visit to the White House?
OL,6,FThat's only something the prime
OL,7,Fminister can do. And Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fhas been at the receiving end of
OL,9,FDonald Trump's ire on a number of
OL,10,Foccasions in recent weeks.
OL,12,FThe Labour chair of the influential
OL,13,FForeign Affairs Committee, Dame Emily
OL,14,FThornberry, has become the latest high-
OL,15,Fprofile politician to call for the
OL,16,Fvisit to be delayed, or even cancelled.
OL,18,FShe said: "The last thing we want to
OL,19,Fdo is have Their Majesties
OL,20,Fembarrassed."
OL,26,@zD@KOU|D@MO]
