OL,3,CShould the UK cancel or delay King's
OL,4,Cstate visit to the White House?
OL,6,FThe MP told BBC Radio 4: "I think it
OL,7,Fneeds to be thought through very
OL,8,Fcarefully as to whether or not it's
OL,9,Fappropriate to go ahead now or maybe
OL,10,Fhave a limited programme or delay it.
OL,11,FBut we can't just pretend there isn't
OL,12,Fa background of war."
OL,14,FThere has been lots of debate about
OL,15,Fthe King's and Queen's visit to the US
OL,16,Fin recent weeks, even though neither
OL,17,Fnation has officially announced it.
OL,19,FPresident Trump has said on Air Force
OL,20,FOne that King Charles is "coming to
OL,21,Four country".
OL,26,@nD@ZOUtD@UO]|D@ZOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
