OL,3,CShould the UK cancel or delay King's
OL,4,Cstate visit to the White House?
OL,6,FITV News understands the provisional
OL,7,Fdates are the end of April, and no one
OL,8,Fknows, not even senior White House
OL,9,Fstaff, what will be happening in the
OL,10,FMiddle East at that time.
OL,12,FDespite being a huge admirer of the
OL,13,FRoyal Family, and therefore very keen
OL,14,Fto host the King and Queen at the
OL,15,FWhite House, the US President has also
OL,16,Fbeen saying some very unflattering
OL,17,Fthings about the British Prime
OL,18,FMinister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
