PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773821068
OL,3,CShould the UK cancel or delay King's
OL,4,Cstate visit to the White House?
OL,6,FPostponing the trip could be explained
OL,7,Fas a logical move given the intensity
OL,8,Fof the war effort for the Trump
OL,9,Fadministration.
OL,11,FCancelling, however, would leave
OL,12,Ftransatlantic relations in a state of
OL,13,Fparalysis.
OL,15,FGiven Trump's propensity for holding
OL,16,Fonto a grudge, the much-talked-about
OL,17,FUK-US "special relationship" would
OL,18,Flikely remain in the deep freeze until
OL,19,Fthe end of his presidential term in
OL,20,Fearly 2029.
